// ââ Evaluate Outcomes + build Telegram message ââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââ
const tickerRaw = $('Fetch BTC Price').first().json;
const tickerResult = tickerRaw && tickerRaw.result ? tickerRaw.result : {};
const tickerKey = Object.keys(tickerResult)[0];
const ticker = tickerResult[tickerKey] || {};
const currentPrice = ticker.c ? parseFloat(ticker.c[0]) : 0;
if (currentPrice === 0) {
  const errMsg = '\uD83D\uDEA8 <b>OUTCOME TRACKER \u2014 ERROR</b>\n\nBTC price fetch failed. Cannot evaluate outcomes.\n\n<i>System continues monitoring.</i>';
  return [{ json: { error: 'No BTC price available', hitRate: 0, evaluated: 0, summary: 'OUTCOME ERROR: BTC price unavailable', telegramMsg: errMsg } }];
}

const vaultRaw = $('Read Vault Signals').first().json;
const memories = (vaultRaw && vaultRaw.memories) ? vaultRaw.memories : [];
const cutoff48h = new Date(Date.now() - 48 * 3600 * 1000).toISOString();

let correct = 0, incorrect = 0, neutral = 0, tooSoon = 0, stale = 0;
const outcomes = [];

for (const mem of memories) {
  const content = mem.content || '';
  const createdAt = mem.created_at || '';
  if (createdAt && createdAt < cutoff48h) { stale++; continue; }
  const dirMatch   = content.match(/TRADE SIGNAL[^:]*:\s*(BUY|SELL|WAIT)\s+BTC/);
  const priceMatch = content.match(/@ \$([\d,]+(?:\.\d+)?)/);
  const confMatch  = content.match(/Confidence:([\d.]+)%/);
  if (!dirMatch || !priceMatch) continue;
  const dir = dirMatch[1];
  const signalPrice = parseFloat(priceMatch[1].replace(/,/g, ''));
  const conf = confMatch ? parseFloat(confMatch[1]) : 50;
  if (dir === 'WAIT') { neutral++; continue; }
  if (signalPrice === 0) continue;
  const ageSecs = createdAt ? (Date.now() - new Date(createdAt).getTime()) / 1000 : 14400;
  const minMove = ageSecs < 3600 ? 0.3 : ageSecs < 14400 ? 0.6 : 1.2;
  const pctMove = ((currentPrice - signalPrice) / signalPrice) * 100;
  let outcome;
  if (Math.abs(pctMove) < minMove) {
    outcome = 'TOO_SOON'; tooSoon++;
  } else if (dir === 'BUY' && pctMove > 0) {
    outcome = 'CORRECT'; correct++;
  } else if (dir === 'SELL' && pctMove < 0) {
    outcome = 'CORRECT'; correct++;
  } else {
    outcome = 'INCORRECT'; incorrect++;
  }
  outcomes.push({ dir, signalPrice, currentPrice: Math.round(currentPrice), pctMove: Math.round(pctMove * 100) / 100, conf, outcome, ageMins: Math.round(ageSecs / 60) });
}

const gradeable    = correct + incorrect;
const hitRate      = gradeable > 0 ? Math.round((correct / gradeable) * 100) : 0;
const graded       = outcomes.filter(o => o.outcome !== 'TOO_SOON');
const avgConf      = graded.length > 0 ? Math.round(graded.reduce((s, o) => s + o.conf, 0) / graded.length * 10) / 10 : 0;
const evaluated    = correct + incorrect + neutral + tooSoon;
const recentGraded = graded.slice(0, 3);
const dataQuality  = gradeable < 5 ? 'INSUFFICIENT' : gradeable < 10 ? 'BUILDING' : 'SUFFICIENT';
const threshold    = 55;

const summary = 'OUTCOME REPORT | ' + new Date().toISOString().slice(0,16) + 'Z\nBTC @ $' + Math.round(currentPrice) +
  '\nEvaluated: ' + evaluated + ' (' + gradeable + ' gradeable, ' + tooSoon + ' too-soon, ' + stale + ' stale, ' + neutral + ' waits)' +
  '\nHit Rate: ' + hitRate + '% (' + correct + '/' + gradeable + ' graded) | Avg Confidence: ' + avgConf + '%' +
  '\nLast 3 graded: ' + (recentGraded.map(o => o.dir + ' ' + o.outcome + ' (' + o.pctMove + '%)').join(' | ') || 'none yet');

// ââ Build Telegram Message ââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââââ
const ts    = new Date().toISOString().replace('T', ' ').slice(0, 16) + ' UTC';
const HR    = '\u2501'.repeat(20);
const hrBadge   = hitRate >= 70 ? '\uD83D\uDD25' : hitRate >= 55 ? '\u2705' : hitRate > 0 ? '\u26A0\uFE0F' : '\uD83D\uDCCA';
const hrStatus  = hitRate >= threshold ? '\u2705 Above ' + threshold + '% threshold' : hitRate > 0 ? '\u26A0\uFE0F Below ' + threshold + '% \u2014 paper mode only' : '\uD83D\uDCCA Accumulating data';
const dqBadge   = dataQuality === 'SUFFICIENT' ? '\uD83D\uDFE2' : dataQuality === 'BUILDING' ? '\uD83D\uDFE1' : '\uD83D\uDD34';

const outcomeLines = recentGraded.map(o => {
  const ico = o.outcome === 'CORRECT' ? '\u2705' : '\u274C';
  const dir2 = o.dir === 'BUY' ? '\uD83D\uDFE2 BUY' : '\uD83D\uDD34 SELL';
  return ico + ' ' + dir2 + '  $' + o.signalPrice.toLocaleString('en-US') + '  \u2192  ' + (o.pctMove >= 0 ? '+' : '') + o.pctMove + '%  (' + o.ageMins + 'min)';
});

const telegramMsg = [
  '\uD83D\uDCCA <b>PERFORMANCE UPDATE \u2014 CRYPTO v3</b>',
  '\uD83D\uDDD3 ' + ts,
  '',
  HR,
  hrBadge + ' <b>HIT RATE: ' + hitRate + '%</b>   (' + correct + ' correct / ' + gradeable + ' graded)',
  hrStatus,
  HR,
  '',
  '\uD83D\uDCB0 BTC: <b>$' + Math.round(currentPrice).toLocaleString('en-US') + '</b>',
  '\uD83D\uDCE6 Avg Signal Confidence: <b>' + avgConf + '%</b>',
  '',
  '<b>Breakdown:</b>',
  '\u2705 Correct: <b>' + correct + '</b>   \u274C Incorrect: <b>' + incorrect + '</b>   \u23F3 Too-soon: <b>' + tooSoon + '</b>',
  '\u26AA Wait signals: <b>' + neutral + '</b>   \uD83D\uDCC5 Stale (>48h): <b>' + stale + '</b>',
  '',
  '<b>Last graded signals:</b>',
  outcomeLines.length ? outcomeLines.join('\n') : '<i>No graded signals yet</i>',
  '',
  dqBadge + ' Data quality: <b>' + dataQuality + '</b>  (' + gradeable + ' graded signals)',
  '',
  '<i>\u23F1 Evaluated every 4h  \u00B7  Threshold: ' + threshold + '%  \u00B7  v3-super</i>'
].join('\n');

return [{ json: { summary, hitRate, correct, incorrect, neutral, tooSoon, stale, evaluated, gradeable, currentPrice, avgConf, outcomes: outcomes.slice(0, 10), dataQuality, telegramMsg } }];

